OL,3,CShoplifting driving abuse of retail
OL,4,Cworkers as 69% report threats at work
OL,6,FITV News Consumer Editor Chris Choi
OL,7,Freports on warnings that shops are
OL,8,Fincreasingly being targeted by
OL,9,Forganised crime gangs
OL,11,FJonathan Sharpells has worked in
OL,12,Fretail for 14 years. During that time,
OL,13,Fhe has faced verbal and physical
OL,14,Fabuse, and was once attacked by four
OL,15,Fpeople at work in an armed robbery.
OL,17,F"That was over in 67 seconds," he told
OL,18,FITV News. "But it felt a bit longer at
OL,19,Fthe time, I can tell you."
