OL,3,CShoplifting driving abuse of retail
OL,4,Cworkers as 69% report threats at work
OL,6,FJonathan's experience is not an
OL,7,Fisolated one. He is among a growing
OL,8,Fnumber of shop workers who have become
OL,9,Fvictims of intimidation and abuse in
OL,10,Fthe past year, according to new
OL,11,Ffigures from the Union of Shop,
OL,12,FDistributive and Allied Workers
OL,13,F(USDAW).
OL,15,FThe union's research has found almost
OL,16,Fone fifth of shop workers have been
OL,17,Fassaulted between 2023 and 2024.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
