OL,3,CShoplifting driving abuse of retail
OL,4,Cworkers as 69% report threats at work
OL,6,F"If you've worked in retail for a
OL,7,Flittle while and if it's not happened
OL,8,Fto you, it's happened to one of your
OL,9,Ffriends," Jonathan told ITV News.
OL,11,FUSDAW have also revealed 69% of shop
OL,12,Fstaff have experienced verbal abuse,
OL,13,Fand around 45% reported being
OL,14,Fthreatened at work.
OL,16,FThe majority of these incidents of
OL,17,Fabuse have been triggered by
OL,18,Fshoplifting, the union found - an
OL,19,Fissue which is itself at a 20-year
OL,20,Fhigh in England and Wales.
