OL,6,FPolice investigating organised crime
OL,7,Fin retail have identified at least 23
OL,8,Fshoplifting gangs operating across the
OL,9,Fcountry, who have stolen an estimated
OL,10,F#3.5 million worth of goods.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FKaty Bourne, Police and Crime
OL,18,FCommissioner for Sussex, is leading
OL,19,Fthe government's taskforce on retail
OL,20,Fcrime - and has said headway has been
OL,21,Fmade in tracking down the gangs.
