OL,6,F"Already we've tracked over 200
OL,7,Findividuals have been identified who
OL,8,Fweren't even on police records
OL,9,Fbefore," she told ITV News.
OL,11,F"So for the first time ever, police
OL,12,Fare able to map those organised crime
OL,13,Fgangs operating across the retail
OL,14,Fsector, and we're already starting to
OL,15,Fsee convictions."
